<h2>What is VaultMill?</h2>

<p>
VaultMill is an executive intelligence platform that organizes
verified public information into clear, structured profiles.
Whether you're researching a CEO, board member, founder, or
industry leader, the goal is to make reliable information easier
to find and understand.
